{"type":null,"faqId":7028,"title":"在雷击多发区，经常发现雷雨过后，有大量的Modem损坏，无法使用？","answer":"在对许多地区的坏猫分析后，发现打雷过后，Modem的以太网损坏了。以太网口一般均设计为户内使用，防雷功能很弱。那为什么打雷会把以太网口给打坏了呢？那是因为许多地区存在多个用户共享使用一个Modem上网的方式。以太网线从窗户穿过，暴露在室外，因此，只要打雷，就很容易打坏Modem的以太网以及计算机网卡。建议运营商在放号时要求用户不能这样使用，否则后果自负。","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7168","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1309501154000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":36,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}